Maintainer: AndresMpa <ing.andres.m.prieto@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/AndresMpa/lyra
Description: Lyra AI assistant for GNU/Linux
 Lyra is a local AI assistant that runs on GNU/Linux systems.
 It includes a FastAPI backend server and an Electron desktop UI.
 After installation, run 'lyra-install-backend' to download
 the AI model appropriate for your hardware.
